    %% ===== RUNTIME FLOW — ADMIN APP =====
    Users --> DNS_App
    DNS_App --> Amplify
    Amplify -->|"API calls<br/>/api/*"| APIGW
    APIGW --> Lambda
    Lambda --> RDS
    RDS --- DataModel

    %% ===== AUTH FLOW =====
    Amplify -.->|"Login / JWT"| Cognito
    Cognito -.->|"Token validation"| AuthMW
    AuthMW -.-> Lambda

    %% ===== RUNTIME FLOW — LAUNCH SITE =====
    Visitors --> DNS_Root
    DNS_Root --> CF_Launch
    CF_Launch --> S3_Launch
    S3_Launch -->|"checkout.js<br/>script.js"| APIGW_Launch
    APIGW_Launch --> Lambda_Checkout
    APIGW_Launch --> Lambda_Contact
    Lambda_Checkout --> Stripe
    Lambda_Contact --> Resend

    %% ===== DEPLOYMENT FLOW =====
    Dev --> GitHub
    GitHub -->|"git push"| AmplifyBuild
    AmplifyBuild -->|"Builds & deploys"| Amplify
    GitHub -->|"git push triggers"| GHA
    GHA -->|"sam deploy"| S3_Artifacts
    S3_Artifacts --> CFN
    CFN -->|"Updates"| Lambda
    CFN -->|"Updates"| APIGW

